description: Lists all inference executions that have been performed by the specified inference scheduler.

parameters.name: InferenceSchedulerName
parameters.description: The name of the inference scheduler for the inference execution listed.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: An opaque pagination token indicating where to continue the listing of inference executions.

nested_items.name: InferenceExecutionSummaries
nested_items.description: Provides an array of information about the individual inference executions returned from the ListInferenceExecutions operation, including model used, inference scheduler, data configuration, and so on.

nested_items.name: ModelName
nested_items.description: The name of the machine learning model being used for the inference execution.

nested_items.name: ModelArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the machine learning model used for the inference execution.

nested_items.name: InferenceSchedulerName
nested_items.description: The name of the inference scheduler being used for the inference execution.

nested_items.name: InferenceSchedulerArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the inference scheduler being used for the inference execution.

nested_items.name: ScheduledStartTime
nested_items.description: Indicates the start time at which the inference scheduler began the specific inference execution.

nested_items.name: DataStartTime
nested_items.description: Indicates the time reference in the dataset at which the inference execution began.

nested_items.name: DataEndTime
nested_items.description: Indicates the time reference in the dataset at which the inference execution stopped.

nested_items.name: DataInputConfiguration
nested_items.description: Specifies configuration information for the input data for the inference scheduler, including delimiter, format, and dataset location.

nested_items.name: S3InputConfiguration
nested_items.description: Specifies configuration information for the input data for the inference, including Amazon S3 location of input data.

nested_items.name: Bucket
nested_items.description: The bucket containing the input dataset for the inference.

nested_items.name: Prefix
nested_items.description: The prefix for the S3 bucket used for the input data for the inference.

nested_items.name: InputTimeZoneOffset
nested_items.description: Indicates the difference between your time zone and Coordinated Universal Time (UTC).

nested_items.name: InferenceInputNameConfiguration
nested_items.description: Specifies configuration information for the input data for the inference, including timestamp format and delimiter.

nested_items.name: TimestampFormat
nested_items.description: The format of the timestamp, whether Epoch time, or standard, with or without hyphens (-).

nested_items.name: ComponentTimestampDelimiter
nested_items.description: Indicates the delimiter character used between items in the data.

nested_items.name: DataOutputConfiguration
nested_items.description: Specifies configuration information for the output results from for the inference execution, including the output Amazon S3 location.

nested_items.name: S3OutputConfiguration
nested_items.description: Specifies configuration information for the output results from for the inference, output S3 location.

nested_items.name: Bucket
nested_items.description: The bucket containing the output results from the inference.

nested_items.name: Prefix
nested_items.description: The prefix for the S3 bucket used for the output results from the inference.

nested_items.name: KmsKeyId
nested_items.description: The ID number for the KMS key key used to encrypt the inference output.

nested_items.name: CustomerResultObject
nested_items.description: The S3 object that the inference execution results were uploaded to.

nested_items.name: Bucket
nested_items.description: The name of the specific S3 bucket.

nested_items.name: Key
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services Key Management Service (KMS key) key being used to encrypt the S3 object. Without this key, data in the bucket is not accessible.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: Indicates the status of the inference execution.

nested_items.name: FailedReason
nested_items.description: Specifies the reason for failure when an inference execution has failed.

nested_items.name: ModelVersion
nested_items.description: The model version used for the inference execution.

nested_items.name: ModelVersionArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Number (ARN) of the model version used for the inference execution.
